    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, it\u2019s super reliable and ready to hit the road. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I just know the next owner is going to love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
