      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic presence, this model has been serviced to rigorous standards to ensure continued performance. It offers a balanced synthesis of engineering excellence and long-term reliability. We invite serious inquiries to evaluate this well-preserved example, which stands as a testament to quality care and sophisticated automotive value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
