    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! If you're looking for something dependable that still looks great and is super comfortable for daily commutes or weekend trips, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
