      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Engineered for the purist, this 996.2 Carrera utilizes the 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus for a broad torque curve and high-revving performance. The G96 6-speed transaxle provides tactile shifts, paired with a chassis featuring Bilstein B8 dampers and upgraded sway bar links for neutral handling. Critical preventative maintenance is documented, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a new water pump. The naturally aspirated induction note remains visceral under load. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s specimen, prioritizing throttle response and lateral grip over showroom aesthetics.",
